nodes.text: The western spaceport was a spaceport in the Port Quarter of the planet Coruscant. During the Separatist Crisis, it experienced, along with the eastern spaceport, a 6,000% increase in migration traffic. During this period, Galactic Republic Senator Padmé Amidala and Jedi Padawan Anakin Skywalker boarded the AA-9 Freighter-Liner Jendirian Valley to Naboo.
